title: Handel - Concerti Grossi, Op. 6 - Karajan, BPO
description:
Handel: 12 Concerti Grosso, Op. 6.

Here is a recording of one of the greatest documents of Baroque Music. And yet I must tell you in advance that this recording of the Op. 6 Concerti Grossi of Handel is the exact opposite of a so called 'period performance'. These recordings were made in the late 1960s by Karajan and the Berlin Philharmonic over the course  of a few summer vacations together (!) They were released on 3 CDs in the early 1990s by DG.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
